      Name          "<html><body>\n<p>For MUR1520G, from datasheet:</p>\n<p>Vf"
" at 25 degrees = 1.05V</p>\n<p>Using the graph for the same diode at 25 degre"
"es in the linear region,</p>\n<p>the instantenous values at some of the point"
"s are:</p>\n<p>Vf =0.6V</p>\n<p>If = 0.4A</p>\n<p>Therefore, Ron = 0.6/0.4 = "
"1.5 Ohms</p></body></html>"
      Position      [245, 295]
    } 
